workers clean 2,607,468 square feet of space. Normal working hours are Monday thru Friday from 12:30 am to 9:00 am. Additionally, some staff work Monday through Friday from 10:00 am to 6:30 pm servicing restrooms and responding to emergencies. For additional cleaning requests contact the Custodial Services office at 940-369-7315 or 940-369-7311. Fiscal Years 2002 through 2010 Compacted Solid Waste Report   TASKS AND FREQUENCIES CLASSROOMS OFFICES RESTROOMS HALLS AND ENTRANCES STAIRWELLS Daily Daily Daily Daily Daily Trash emptied Empty and clean trash receptacles Empty and clean trash receptacles Trash emptied Swept and spot mopped Swept and spot mopped Clean door glass Sweep and mop floor with disinfectant Swept and spot mopped   Spot vacuumed Disinfect door handles Disinfect all solid surfaces Spot vacuumed   Chalk and marker boards cleaned   Spot clean partitions with disinfectant Clean glass   Pencil sharpener emptied   Restock toilet tissue and paper towels     Student desks arranged   Fill empty soap dispensers     Door handles and glass cleaned and disinfected                   Weekly Weekly   Weekly Weekly Mop all hard surface floors Vacuum complete carpeted area   Mop all hard surface floors Mop all hard surface floors Vacuum all carpeted surfaces Sweep and mop hard floors   Vacuum all carpeted surfaces Dust ledges Dust open areas of shelves and desks Dust open areas of shelves and desks                 As Needed As Needed Semi Annual or as needed As Needed   Spot clean student desks Spot clean carpets Disinfect walls Spot clean walls   Spot clean carpet Strip and was hard floor surfaces Dust ceiling vents Spot clean carpet   Strip and wax hard floor surfaces Shampoo carpets Strip and wax floors Burnish tile   Shampoo carpet Dust blinds   Dust ceiling vents   Dust blinds Dust ceiling vents       Dust ceiling vents          Downloads AttachmentSize Crew Leader Assignments (PDF)78.83 KB Construction Report The monthly Construction Obstruction Report shows you